FAQ

Frequently Asked Questions

Everything you need to know.

About Preshent

What is Preshent?

Preshent is a sustainability-focused platform that integrates AI, blockchain, and finance to help communities, businesses, and governments deploy projects with trust and efficiency. From clean energy to infrastructure and finance, we provide tools to simplify complex programs while ensuring compliance and measurable impact.

What are the core areas of Preshent’s business?

Preshent operates across four interconnected areas:

  • Preshent OS – A global system that connects buyers, suppliers, and programs for seamless collaboration.

  • Ventures – Large-scale deployments such as Tribal Sovereign Energy and REAC.

  • JR AI – Our intelligence engine that ensures compliance, verifies suppliers, and guides smarter decisions.

  • Finance (PRSH Token) – A digital settlement and rewards system that links funding to verified milestones.

Preshent OS

How does Preshent OS work?

Preshent OS acts as a digital infrastructure hub where buyers, suppliers, and administrators can collaborate in one environment. It streamlines project onboarding, compliance checks, supplier matching, milestone verification, and settlement.

Who can use Preshent OS?

Preshent OS is designed for enterprises, government agencies, suppliers, developers, and community programs. Whether you’re installing renewable energy systems, funding infrastructure, or managing compliance, OS provides a single point of truth.

JR AI

What is JR AI?

JR AI is our compliance-driven intelligence engine. It automates verification processes, checks certifications, ensures regulatory compliance, and guides users through program participation. JR AI reduces risk and improves efficiency across all transactions.

Does JR AI replace humans in the process?

No. JR AI augments decision-making by handling repetitive compliance and verification tasks. Final decisions remain with project owners, buyers, and administrators.

Finance & PRSH

What is PRSH?

PRSH is Preshent’s digital asset built on Base and used for settlement, rewards, and rebates. It links project funding to verified milestones and enables secure, transparent transactions across Preshent OS.

How are rebates handled?

Rebates are issued in PRSH tokens once specific project milestones are verified by JR AI. This ensures that incentives are tied directly to real-world impact.

Can I use currencies other than PRSH?

Yes. Buyers and investors can transact in fiat currencies (such as USD) or stablecoins, with PRSH used for settlement, rebates, and incentive distribution.

Ventures & Programs

What are Preshent Ventures?

Ventures are large-scale programs that Preshent drives in partnership with communities, governments, and enterprises. These include renewable energy deployments, infrastructure development, and sustainability finance initiatives.

How does Preshent support Tribal Nations?

Preshent collaborates directly with Tribal Nations on energy sovereignty programs, deploying renewable power, resilient infrastructure, and rebate-backed financing. Our goal is to deliver long-term sustainability and economic empowerment.

Security & Compliance

How does Preshent ensure compliance?

Compliance is built into every stage of the process through JR AI. It verifies certifications, enforces local regulations, and ties funding to verified outcomes.

How secure are transactions on Preshent?

All transactions are executed via blockchain-based smart contracts, ensuring transparency, traceability, and security. Wallets and accounts are verified through industry-standard KYC/KYB processes.

Getting Started

How can I join Preshent as a buyer, supplier, or investor?

You can register on Preshent OS, create a verified wallet, and complete compliance onboarding through JR AI. From there, you’ll gain access to pools, projects, and opportunities tailored to your role.

How do I stay updated on Preshent’s progress?

Follow our official channels (Telegram, X, LinkedIn, Discord, and website updates) for announcements, program launches, and token milestones.
